Final Crisis - Legion of Three Worlds HC (2009-10) (digital) (OkC.O.M.P.U.T.O.-Novus-HD)


As Darkseid wages a war of evil in the far future of FINAL CRISIS, the Legion of Super-Heroes and the Man of Steel contend with colliding timelines and the villainous Time Trapper! Geoff Johns (GREEN LANTERN) teams with George Perez (AVENGERS, JUSTICE LEAGUE OF AMERICA) for a legendary Legion tale!


Thanks goes to OkC.O.M.P.U.T.O for this release.
